  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Girls Live Healthy with Effective Pad Usage</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Chhaupadi, the traditional act of banishing women (during their periods) from houses, schools, etc. is still widely practiced. Nepalese people lack the adequate knowledge and information regarding the need to maintain menstrual hygiene, which may lead to serious reproductive health issues. Our project has a clear goal. We will provide the production of low cost pads and transformational hygiene education to 5000 young women.</narrative>
  </description>
